snippet.title: Cat Warfare Trailer - 5th Year Update
snippet.description:
This is Cat Warfare's 5th year being on Steam!


Cat Warfare is a multiplayer first person shooter that lets you take the place of a cat out for revenge, blood and glory.

Play the game: https://store.steampowered.com/app/923370/Cat_Warfare/
Join our discord: https://discord.gg/TmrMx8P
Twitter: https://twitter.com/NSClassicGames

Good luck and its going to be one heck of a cat fight.
Don't forget to subscribe!

#NotSoClassicGames
#CatWarfare
